Installation
================


Python ``pip`` package is required to install ``spb``.


From sources
------------

Use the following command line to install ``spb`` from sources directory (containing setup.py):

    git clone https://github.com/patsuckow/spb
    cd spb
    pip install -r requirements.txt
    python setup.py install


From PyPI
---------

Alternatively you can install ``spb`` from PyPI:

    pip install spb

